import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    data = data.dropna()
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    ax.plot(data['date'], data['price'])
    ax.set_xlabel('Date')
    ax.set_ylabel('Price')
    ax.set_title('What is the trend of S&P 500 prices over time?')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['price'].plot(kind='hist', bins=50, color='blue', edgecolor='black', alpha=0.7)
    plt.axvline(data['price'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Mean: {data['price'].mean():0.2f}")
    plt.axvline(data['price'].median(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Median: {data['price'].median():0.2f}")
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of S&P 500 prices?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    data = data.dropna()
    avg_price = data.groupby('date')['price'].mean()
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    ax.plot(avg_price.index, avg_price.values, color='blue')
    ax.axhline(y=avg_price.mean(), color='red', linestyle='--', label=f'Average Price: {avg_price.mean():.2f}')
    ax.legend(loc='best')
    plt.title('What is the average price of S&P 500 over the given time period?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    ax.boxplot(data['price'], vert=False)
    ax.set_title('What is the volatility of S&P 500 prices?')
    ax.axvline(data['price'].median(), color='r', label=f'Median: {data["price"].median():.2f}')
    ax.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
